  from vhci_map_urb_for_dma() which is removed in v6 to
  vhci_send_cmd_submit().

- Add clearing URB_DMA_MAP_SG flag before vhci gives back URB to
  itâ€™s driver to avoid dma unmapping in hcd_unmap_urb_for_dma().

